  <summary>5/19/2006--Introduced.
Recognizes the effects of harmful algal blooms (including Red Tide) on the environment and the need for federal, state, territorial, and local agencies and other research institutions to solve the increasing problems facing coastal areas from its harmful effects. Commends public and private organizations that are researching the ongoing problem of harmful algal blooms.</summary>
